Applying filter on OData and Viz-Chart # This is an example of Viz-Charts with line-chart with filters. There are a lot of techniques this is one to solve the filtering issue.
Point to be noted is that you need to bind the Dataset of VizFrame by its ID and then apply the filtering on the FlattenedDataset In the controller:
// defining the Filter var oFilter = new sap.ui.model.Filter(&quot;Data1&quot;,sap.ui.model.FilterOperator.GT,10); //Setting oModel var oModel = new sap.
